race.comment: EL MORZILLO (3) wasn't disgraced in Group 1 company before the spell and will find this assignment much more to her liking. Tuned up for this with a recent trial placing and has a bit of class over this field. Gets 3kg off and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. READY TO SCHIPP (4) got the job done at the Sunny Coast last time out and Franklin stays in the saddle. Again gets the benefit of his claim and should get a soft run from the inside marble. Capable of playing a major role. ALECTRONA (1) is on the doorstep of another victory with four consecutive runner-up finishes. Can go one better against this line-up. SIRKEL (8) returned in good order with a solid win around this circuit and the step-up to the 1350m suits. In the mix. MORE FOR READY (7) next best in a race with only a handful of chances.
